title: The Masked Singer: Unmasked
overview: ITV is launching The Masked Singer: Unmasked, which will be hosted by Capital Xtra presenter Will Njobvu and air exclusively on ITV Hub.The show will include exclusive first interview with each evening's unmasked celebrity, backstage gossip with panelists Jonathan Ross, Davina McCall, Rita Ora and Mo Gilligan, as well as other behind-the-scenes bits.
